data.description: The beautiful, immaculately keep single story full brick ranch-style home, is a MUST SEE! Floorplan is functional and well-designed, living room has airy high ceilings and open to the formal dining area, perfect for gatherings. The kitchen offers ample counter top space and a breakfast nook. Great size master bedroom and additional bedrooms. This property screams pride of ownership. The yard has been very well maintains and is HUGE, great for entertaining and outdoor activities. This amazing property is waiting or a lucky new owner. Schedule your private showing today!
